The '''xinkra''' were fearsome three-meter tall predators native to [[Kushibah]], also home to the lagomorph [[Kushiban]] species. They were feared by the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] other species, particularly the Kushiban. Xinkra could be driven away by fire, the only thing they feared. The [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Ikrit]] saved his village from a pack of xinkra by using [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] to convince the creatures to seek food elsewhere.

